## 17. Integration with Template Engine

### Dynamic Sections

| Template Variable | Purpose                  |
| ----------------- | ------------------------ |
| `mapvars`         | Sweep data               |
| `mapvars_dim`     | Determines 2D vs 3D      |
| `mappings`        | Parameter assignments    |
| `scopes`          | Scope list               |
| `simstruct_line`  | Simulation configuration |
| `results_folder`  | Output directory         |

---

## 18. Best Practices

* ✅ Always enable `CLEAR_TRACES` for batch runs
* ✅ Use descriptive parameter names in `mappings`
* ✅ Keep scope list updated with model changes
* ✅ Validate `data` dimensions before execution
* ✅ Use version-controlled templates

